data.description:
Experience the pinnacle of urban living in this top-floor oasis with breathtaking city and water garden views. Nestled in a modern mid-rise, it's a testament to luxury and convenience. Built from the ground up on a historic site, this unit boasts an elevator for effortless access and a gated parking structure for your peace of mind. the convenience of living downtown within walking distance to shopping an dinning.
The generously sized kitchen features exquisite granite countertops, making meal prep a pleasure. Storage is never an issue with a huge closet, and the elegant concrete floors add a touch of sophistication to the space.
